<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>Welcome to XelleNet!</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f8f9fb;
      color: #333;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      background: #fff;
      margin: 40px auto;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
      padding: 24px;
    }
    h1 {
      color: #2d89ef;
      text-align: center;
    }
    p {
      line-height: 1.6;
      font-size: 16px;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      background: #2d89ef;
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      font-weight: 500;
      margin-top: 16px;
    }
    footer {
      margin-top: 32px;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #888;
      text-align: center;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Welcome to {{appName}} 🎉</h1>
    <p>Hi {{firstname}},</p>
    <p>
      Congratulations! Your email has been successfully verified.  
      We're thrilled to have you join our community.
    </p>
    <p>
      You can now explore all features, connect, and start enjoying a seamless experience on XelleNet.
    </p>
    <a href="https://jinva.com/login" class="button">Go to Dashboard</a>

    <footer>
      <p>— The {{appName}} Team</p>
      
      <p>Need help? <a href="mailto:support@jinva.com">Contact Support</a></p>
      © {{year}} {{appName}}. All rights reserved.
    </footer>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
